snippet.title: Don't Kill Rumble - Official Game Overview Trailer | Latin American Games Showcase
snippet.description: Watch the game overview trailer for Don't Kill Rumble, an online multiplayer King of the Hill battle royale game developed by Scubalight Studios. Players will use gadgets and strategic movements to achieve victory by conquering the Tower in a given match. Don't Kill Rumble is coming soon to PC (Steam).
